# Npub watchlist for Hermes bot responsibility #8 (repo mirroring).
# Add one npub per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# These are the Nostr public keys whose repos the mirror bot will
# clone + continuously fetch so nothing is lost if grasp-server /
# ngit relays become unreachable.
#
# Example format:
#   npub1abcdef...
#   npub123456...
#
# After editing, the mirror job (B7, not yet built) reads this file.
